07/02/2011
TIRANA, Albania -- Police on Sunday (February 6th) blocked the transportation of 15kg of marijuana that was heading to Greece. 
The stash was hidden in vehicle wheels. 
Several days earlier, another drug smuggler was arrested on a bus to Athens.
Meanwhile, police in Ioannina, Greece seized 100kg of marijuana believed to have entered the country from Albania. 
(Klan, Balkan Web, Top News, Telegrafi - 06/02/11)
